ATTRIBUTION

kRouter is a hardened fork of 9router (https://github.com/decolua/9router).
All original architecture, providers, dashboard, and core feature work were
authored by decolua and the upstream contributors. This fork, maintained by
Kodelyth AI Infrastructure, adds production-hardening fixes (security, MITM
stream reliability, Antigravity ban handling, real-time quota tracking) and
ports compatible improvements from related projects (OmniRoute v3.8+) on top
of the upstream baseline.

⭐ Please star the upstream project: https://github.com/decolua/9router
